To plot indicator values, in the OnData event handler, call the Plot method.

private LogReturn _logr;

// In Initialize()
var symbol = AddEquity("SPY").Symbol;
_logr = LOGR(symbol, period);

// In OnData()
if (_logr.IsReady)
{
    Plot("My Indicators", "logreturn", _logr.Current.Value);
}
